Name: Yuzi Lims: anime runner
About the game: Yuzi Lims: anime runner is an endless runner in the anime style. The mission of player is to help the girl Yusi Lims trying reach his dreams, avoiding obstacles. - Beautiful graphic in the style of anime - Pleasant music - Endless gameplay - Steam achievements Controls: Arrows and space bar Credits: This game was created using Clickteam Fusion 2.5! Music by Erwarda Savitnaag.
